name: Wee Xiang Cafe

reviews.text: The food was really really really bad the egg tofu was. Terrible we are unable to eat pork and forced us to get the pork one despite us telling us the egg tofu is white and the prawns in the egg tofu looks white and uncooked the cereal prawn is terrible very very bad super terrible the first soup is tastless and bland the chicken in the egg tofu is lioe saw flavour less tarrible

My family and I just went there to eat - meat dishes + kang kong & hotplate tofu. It was overall a delightful meal because of very pleasant staff, aircon and peaceful atmosphere. Food is not as great as those outside coffee shop zi char but it still tastes nice and is healthier which we like. Great local drink options too.
Limited selection but if you are lazy to go elsewhere, this is quite a good place to eat.   Honestly the tze char can pass!  I was truly surprised.  There's also other food as shown in my photos.

Convenient and family friendly place for food, best part is that it is air-conditioned. A lot of room for improvement for the food quality, 3 stars for food. 5 stars for the friendly and helpful uncle.
Wow didn't expect the food to taste better than decent. Tried the sambal fried rice today, but have been a good place to eat wantonmee.
